textBeforeTable: Albums[edit] Trina made an appearance at Minnesota Vikings tackle Bryant McKinnie's birthday party and while on stage took shots at fellow female rapper Khia.[67] Following the burglary in his St. Louis mansion, Nelly offers a cash reward for information leading to the arrest of the housebreaker.[66] T.I. was released three months early from prison and was admitted into a halfway house in his hometown of Atlanta.[65] Entertainment Weekly named Kid Cudi's Man on the Moon: The End of Day the best Hip-Hop Album of 2009.[64] Billboard names The Neptunes "Producers Of Decade".[63] Long awaited Lil Wayne album, Rebirth leaks 2 months before release.
